--------------
Command Layout
--------------
Project_H.Type.Action(Count,Text,Password)

---------
Type List
---------
Text #Text is what ever you want to encrypt or decrypt

-----------
Action List
-----------
Encryption #Encryption encrypts what ever you input
Decryption #Decryption decrypts what ever you input

----------
Count List
----------
True #True makes it show the progress of it encrypting and decrypting
False #False makes it so the progress is not shown while encrypting and decrypting the inputs

-----------------
Text and Password
-----------------
Both of these variables are ones that you have to put it the text is the text you want to encrypt or decrypt and the
password that you want to use.